{
  "title": "Intensely Resinous Irish Lamb Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and aromatic Irish lamb stew featuring shichimi-togarashi and a mother-sauce-base, cooked to perfection in a donabe vessel, this dish is diabetic-friendly and perfect for a cozy evening",
